## Checklist

Before going live with email:

- [ ] All email categories your features need are implemented
- [ ] Plain text version exists for every HTML email
- [ ] Emails tested on Gmail, Outlook, Apple Mail, mobile
- [ ] Readable contrast verified across common clients
- [ ] Unsubscribe link works in every applicable email
- [ ] Subscriber preferences accessible (if multi-channel)
- [ ] SPF, DKIM, DMARC records configured
- [ ] Bounce handling implemented
- [ ] Emails queued (not sent synchronously)
- [ ] Retry logic for failed sends
- [ ] No sensitive data in email content
- [ ] Subject lines are specific and under 50 chars
- [ ] Sender name is recognizable (not "noreply")
